data.description: BACK ON THE MARKET - Buyers financing fell through, no fault of the sellers. WELCOME to a homestead slice of heaven situated just 30 minutes east of Raleigh. This 4.5 ACRE FARM has produced and sustained the sole farm business that encompasses flowers, veggies, fruits, cows, sheep, goats, puppies, bunnies and chicken and is chock full of everything the homesteader at heart is looking for *3 FENCED PASTURES*1/4 ACRE POND*LIVESTOCK BARN*NEW FENCING THROUGHOUT*2 Chicken Coops*10 x 20 STORAGE SHED with A/C unit*HUGE 30 x 60 DETACHED GARAGE with overhang and 2 roll up doors, raised garden beds, ample space for the budding flower farmer and a growing ORCHARD with plums, pears, apples, figs and blackberries. This property boasts an updated 3 bedroom, 2 bath rustic farmhouse with a large living room and separate family room, a primary suite with office area or use as a nursery. Enjoy the rocking chair front porch and spacious tiered back deck. A true paradise for the homeowner looking to be more self-sustaining and self-sufficient with NO Restrictions*OVER 3 ACRES OF FENCED PASTURE - wired for electric fence *2 yard hydrants*ROOF installed in 2019* New well pump * Refrigerator/Washer/Dryer included*Conveniently located just 1 mile off Hwy 42. Only 15 minutes to HWY 264, I-95, Flowers Plantation/Clayton and Wilson - home of Buckhorn Reservoir. Come find it all and more. *Note-Use Caution as Fences are electric*
